    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Pirate Gamer has trapped you inside the Arcade Asylum with other gamers. Play through a variety of reimagined classic minigames from diverse genres with varied graphics and unique twists. The catch? You have to be the best across all genres of games to beat out all the other inmates and escape the Asylum.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Arcade Asylum&quot; is the perfect game for online parties, and competitive gamers who crave a blend of chaotic fun and strategic gameplay. Can you prove your skills and smarts to be the first to escape the Arcade Asylum, or will you become another mad denizen of this bizarre world? The Pirate Gamer awaits your attempt to escape!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>HOW TO ESCAPE?</strong>  </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                       <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/aaf88261b067151b689573bba7a5214f.avif?t=1769831783\" width=341 height=97 /></span>       <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/575ea0c57eac5670dea86fe63f87bd4c.poster.avif?t=1769831783\" width=116 height=115 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/575ea0c57eac5670dea86fe63f87bd4c.webm?t=1769831783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>        </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>HOW TO EARN TOKENS?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/ff0d08cfb9c104ec444eee6e830cefa7.poster.avif?t=1769831783\" width=191 height=191 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/ff0d08cfb9c104ec444eee6e830cefa7.webm?t=1769831783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>                <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/29a1fa3394339b8d9434764050faab2f.poster.avif?t=1769831783\" width=197 height=197 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/29a1fa3394339b8d9434764050faab2f.webm?t=1769831783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>                   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/ca3e58761ddd0fe702d84ced15499e44.poster.avif?t=1769831783\" width=197 height=197 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/ca3e58761ddd0fe702d84ced15499e44.webm?t=1769831783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>              Find a portal</strong>                                <strong>Challenge another player                                    Co-op with a player</strong>        </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">      </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Portals lead to Solo Games</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/d666c1048c33250da41b2d71d929a6f8.poster.avif?t=1769831783\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/d666c1048c33250da41b2d71d929a6f8.webm?t=1769831783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/d666c1048c33250da41b2d71d929a6f8.mp4?t=1769831783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hunt down another inmate for Challenge Games</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/49bb5b07cedbd6500265ddd546b6ba39.poster.avif?t=1769831783\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/49bb5b07cedbd6500265ddd546b6ba39.webm?t=1769831783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/49bb5b07cedbd6500265ddd546b6ba39.mp4?t=1769831783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Team up with another for Co-op Games</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/1ae22e93cfa385c5bc8da1cd1988377d.poster.avif?t=1769831783\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/1ae22e93cfa385c5bc8da1cd1988377d.webm?t=1769831783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/1ae22e93cfa385c5bc8da1cd1988377d.mp4?t=1769831783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>                                                  GOT ENOUGH TOKENS?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>                            Find an Escape Portal before the other inmates</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/a55b622424b972ba8c404cc6b7b2a761.poster.avif?t=1769831783\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/a55b622424b972ba8c404cc6b7b2a761.webm?t=1769831783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/a55b622424b972ba8c404cc6b7b2a761.mp4?t=1769831783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                            3 Fun Classes with varied abilities</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>                   Casual                                                 Pro                                                 Streamer                                      </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/fe4d9f6173045a37b9128b7078365cfe.poster.avif?t=1769831783\" width=195 height=195 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/fe4d9f6173045a37b9128b7078365cfe.webm?t=1769831783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>       <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/216cb12aa2f0164c4165b4d5ca049a9d.poster.avif?t=1769831783\" width=195 height=195 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324780/extras/216cb12aa2f0164c4165b4d5ca049a9d.webm?t=1769831783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.